## 🧠 AI Behavior Rules

- **Never assume Odoo version** - Always detect first
- **Never mix Odoo 8 and Odoo 13 syntax** - Use version-appropriate code
- **Always check existing modules** before creating new functionality
- **Never delete or overwrite existing code** unless explicitly instructed
- **Always update security files** when adding new models
- **Always test module upgrade** after making changes
- **Use Odoo's ORM methods** - Don't write raw SQL unless necessary
- **Follow Odoo's security model** - Use access rights and record rules

